cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to build discourse annotated corpora. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses statistical word-alignment models and a classifier, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses filtering out unsupported annotations. Finally, the paper deals with computational linguistics (cs.CY) as it focuses on discourse analysis and annotation.
